      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SWEET PINS NZ (1) finished sixth last start, beaten 13 metres at this track over 2130m. Talented and has plenty of upside. Has the benefit of a good draw and he can figure in the finish. BETTORS PRIDE (4) is a strong fresh performer back after a spell of four months and is yet to have his colours lowered when resuming. Scored a fine win over 2130m here to launch his last preparation. Finds a nice race so anticipating a bright start to this preparation. LINCOLN RIVER NZ (10) is worth another chance after a last-start eighth over 2130m at this circuit a week ago. MINOS NZ (6) disappointed last time but is a chance based on a good third over 2130m at this venue two runs back. Can bounce back.",
